{"tid":1172331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於吞左自己啲精","createTime":"2019-05-26T11:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T12:05:44.000Z","uid":5077,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"736c3f46276554a17842eacb829c12f20c9c7cf7","tid":1172331,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"事源係咁 上上星期顏射咗男朋友 <br />\n之後手痕影左幾張相俾佢發現咗 <br />\n話要我都試下吞精先可以keep啲相<br />\n之後2星期我梗係唔制，每次都推9開佢，話哂都虎毒不吃兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最多都係口爆佢吞完強吻我個陣hi到少少 都算無乜味 係腥腥地<br />\n結果尋日激撚嬲佢 佢今日嬲爆爆格硬捉住我lur咗落黎<br />\n我已經半秒時間都無猶豫咕一聲吞咗去<br />\n結果係好撚奇怪的質感+落喉嚨途中有少少苦<br />\n即刻乾咳左幾下<br />\n佢猛係度笑 仲話已經幫我食咗一半 <br />\n仲問我知道佢有幾偉大未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e5471f57ec258b4cef7812a96aa9c925b675a3","tid":1172331,"uid":167330,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"死基佬收皮啦"},{"pid":"df37d0115b87db01e9193070e1f68a0824e28172","tid":1172331,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"skr wor"},{"pid":"ef43fb9b38beba15b113a66089d564b561687b9b","tid":1172331,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97e765f36af777b387eafbaca70be5650889161","tid":1172331,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NQxJQm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NQxJQm.gif&h=e8d01b07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"912556a388218d9b82c43e4c2873889ec00433c1","tid":1172331,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afwkSJU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafwkSJU.gif&h=a4d66e3b&s={SIZE}\" />"}